NATURE OF MODIFICATIONS:
------------------------
This derivative work (bases_on) contains substantial modifications to the 
original pgAdmin 4 source code, including but not limited to:

  1. Complete UI/UX rebrand with custom dark crimson theme (#7F1D1D)
  2. Custom branding system (branding.py module)
  3. Inter font family integration system-wide
  4. Custom logo assets (SVG gradient logo + PNG variants)
  5. Footer copyright integration on all pages
  6. Modified Material-UI theme configuration
  7. Custom login/security page UI redesign
  8. Docker image restructuring with Alpine Linux optimization
  9. File path modifications (/var/lib/bases_on instead of /var/lib/pgadmin)
  10. Entrypoint script modifications for custom paths

DETAILED MODIFICATION LOG:
--------------------------
